  <name>Tabs</name>
  <summary>View and manage guitar tabs and chords from Freetar</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Tabs is a chords and tabs app for Linux built with GTK4 and Libadwaita.
      Search for songs, add favorites, zoom text, and use the autoscroller for hands-free playing.
      Works offline and adapts to any screen size with a responsive design.
    </p>
  </description>

